column5: I hope everyone has a great holiday season

Thanks guys Turkeys in the Oven my family comes over tonight and then it's off to the wifes Family in the morning the munchkins to open presents and for steak and egg brunch a mix of t-bones and the father-inlaws favorite cut of steak (he's a butcher) and some venison steaks I won't be able to move come boxing day but I have to get up to get my new LED TV on sale it will be worth all the effort cause then I have a week of doing nothing ,Well mabye some fishing
